Hello <%=@user%>,

  This email is to confirm that you scheduled the following meeting:

    Title: <%= @meeting.title %>
    Location: <%= @meeting.location %>
    Start Time: <%= @meeting.start_time %>
    End Time: <%= @meeting.end_time %>
    Room: <%= @meeting.room.name %> (<%= @meeting.room.room_number %>)
    Attendees:
      <% @meeting.employees.each do |employee| %>
        <%= employee.name %>
      <% end %>




Please be sure to arrive on time. Thank you.

Sincerely,
<%= @meeting.employee.company.name %> Management
